➜福奇：特朗普“可能”已获得新冠病毒暂时免疫力，但并非永久
http://www.sohu.com/a/424362605_260616	33330
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
