➜联播+｜心系岭南，细节中感受习近平对广东的深情关怀
http://www.sohu.com/a/424398853_260616	44013
<p><img width="600" src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201013/568d59b26add4aa3be4147dc67a3f1b9.jpeg" /></p>
